<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ طَريِفُ بنُ دَيْسَقٍ التَّمِيمِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - وَفِينَا وَإِنْ قُلْنَا اصْطَلَحْنَا ضَغَائِنٌ ... كَمَا طَرَّ أَوْبَارُ الجِرَابِ عَلَى النَّشْرِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضًا:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - جَنَا الْعَداوَةَ آبَاءٌ لنا سَلَفَتْ ... فَلَنْ تَبِيدَ وَلِلآبَاءِ أَبْنَاءُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ضَمْرَةُ بنُ جَابِرٍ الْحَنَفِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - أَرِيدُونِي إِرَادَتَكُمْ فَإِنِّي ... عَلَى مُرِّ الْعَدَاوَةِ مَا بَقِيتُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢ - نَشَأْتُ بِهَا لَدُنْ أَنّي وَلِيدٌ ... وأُورِثُها بَنيَّ إِذا فَنيِتُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٦٢)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مَعْرُوفُ بنُ عمروٍ الطَّائِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ - إِذَا كَانَ فِي نَفْسِ ابْنِ عَمِّكَ إِحْنَةٌ ... فَلا تَسْتثِرْهَا سَوْف يَبْدُو دَفِينُهَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>